{"tid":1443470,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"2014年 祖兒寸Kay借政治歌上位呃Like  2019年 Kay借民主女神名義上位後不再發聲","createTime":"2019-08-11T08:36:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T21:32:37.000Z","uid":35964,"like":151,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"120d8bfb5d62cfd4f2e3b494424e636bec14f4fa","tid":1443470,"uid":35964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T08:36:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20140704/52656259\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20140704%2F52656259&d=gk%2Bh3YXCSP8KuySO9FkCKi2wsmw0HNSHoQ%2FRl4ZEJbA%3D&h=ef1cb747\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20140704%2F52656259&h=7d94f254\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20140704/52656259</a><br />\n謝安琪（Kay）在7.1前夕，在網上發放新歌《雞蛋與羔羊》，歌詞敏感似為港人發聲，昨日卻傳出該歌曲不讓電台播放，商台證實被拒。Kay的「又要威又要戴頭盔」舉動，辣㷫網民留言寸爆她借勢騎劫政治，發聲歌變抽水歌，連宿敵容祖兒都出手按like寸埋一份。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20140703/large/1404398178_5ea9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20140703%2Flarge%2F1404398178_5ea9.jpg&h=a9c47c98&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n容祖兒一早睇穿技安琪假面具<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當年like個post都比人鬧到狗血淋頭 時間證明民主女神技安琪根本欺世盜名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b721c6f5436f8d8b8a2787209bb1c282414b976","tid":1443470,"uid":176112,"like":5,"dislike":6,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T08:37:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">WFC</span>"},{"pid":"bd9f6b6a82de044196a877